   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 384,
   "width": 1614.17,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Each step gates the next: the workload never goes on until the patch transaction exits 0, exactly three fingerprints are present, root is locked, and `sshd -T` confirms both password methods are off. Run the whole baseline before the host carries anything.",
   "originalText": "Each step gates the next: the workload never goes on until the patch transaction exits 0, exactly three fingerprints are present, root is locked, and `sshd -T` confirms both password methods are off. Run the whole baseline before the host carries anything.",
